# PNA header union example: parses S header, then union member based on S.t.
# Ingress modifies the union data. No send_to_port -> drop.

# S.t=0: parse O1 (1 byte). Ingress sets O1.data=0xff.
packet 0 00 AA

# S.t=1: parse O2 (2 bytes). Ingress sets O2.data=0xffff.
packet 0 01 AABB

# S.t=2: no union member parsed. Drop.
packet 0 02
